{"tid":483954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就炒車一事道歉","createTime":"2017-11-29T15:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T06:54:48.000Z","uid":158975,"like":1,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b83701acc196ad98a90767fe754686c25277e5","tid":483954,"uid":158975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"大家有睇post都知我炒曬車<br />\n我亦係到講聲對唔住<br />\n如果當事人覺得有損失<br />\n我亦可向佢賠償。<br />\n但想大家搞清楚件事<br />\nsam哥一開頭係比上層照肺<br />\n話佢無收到錢<br />\n聯絡舊post圖中人<br />\n不停兜圈 最後仲block埋sam哥電話<br />\n直到件事發大後 <br />\n旅遊巴公司先同sam哥講話收咗錢<br />\n論做事 我係錯 <br />\n但亦希望大家可以諗下旅遊巴公司同租車人溝通問題<br />\n再諗下捉完sam照完肺<br />\n件事發大先再同佢講收咗<br />\n最後對事主講聲 對唔住"},{"pid":"7e63137979b5bce1b986011e5d0a5c1f3417a40a","tid":483954,"uid":158975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"亦要向各位繼續炒車嘅講聲對唔住"},{"pid":"ebde0b77ad21c04a899f89898172d90a8dfd3d2a","tid":483954,"uid":158975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"亦要向各位繼續炒車嘅講聲對唔住"},{"pid":"6efde3d6f5eaa7afa9eb39b53ffaab6015eeab10","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"好心你叫個位阿sam係group到講清楚d啦<br />\n而家係到講d唔講d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831907693d88c023b500bc92bc33adb162994354","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"仲要一嚟未搞清楚就叫個group堆小圈子一人一向新人祝福<br />\n個鍾小姐比你地改哂圖，又係人地fb留哂言屌柒人<br />\n私下你老細一句sorry就算，唔係你老細落order又點有道歉呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/235519_1c6721882818aa653e54c07daaab7e37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F235519_1c6721882818aa653e54c07daaab7e37.png&h=692c45f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2095a9c6c07a360081f1d3f71c9951b4176520f","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/183754_039cc9a32c950a677a1fb74dc26ff538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F183754_039cc9a32c950a677a1fb74dc26ff538.jpg&h=cc0e11da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/183755_4b7245aa70feeb43177fae4c07ce3de2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F183755_4b7245aa70feeb43177fae4c07ce3de2.jpg&h=b53fb627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩張又唔見個位阿sam放上group比其他人睇下？<br />\n好明顯個位阿sam wtsapp個個人同contact 阿伯個個係兩個人啦"},{"pid":"7dd9662c9798e21cfc81eff074827979e4ef7e64","tid":483954,"uid":50565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"係個Group到講D唔講D，而家仲有班盲撐話佢無做錯，自己又唔撚解釋返清楚，屌鳩人就係威係勢，要解釋就帶撚晒頭盔！"},{"pid":"cbea77ddb153120272c7af6b9d40b17d726a31c5","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係個Group到講D唔講D，而家仲有班盲撐話佢無做錯，自己又唔撚解釋返清楚，屌鳩人就係威係勢，要解釋就帶撚晒頭盔！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係，都痴線<br />\n今日改人地圖鬧人地好開心㗎，一柒咗就潛哂水<br />\n連個事主都係圍威喂就咁帶過就算"},{"pid":"02339c9422b65406852259f650795cba64a29f4f","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯絡舊post圖中人<br />\n不停兜圈 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n好明顯人地都唔知發生咩事，都要時間問清楚其他人<br />\n仲要係新人同個女仔都係去咗旅行<br />\n明明錢就比咗，冇啦啦話你比未錢，都要傾返同搵返到底咩事<br />\n睇多次wtsapp對話圖就知道唔係同一個人同阿伯傾啦<br />\n人地block你又話人地有問題，有個痴線佬係咁要求比錢交代本來比咗錢嘅事<br />\n唔block柒你就奇啦"},{"pid":"bcdd6e42973cb3e4485b2d42abba569228d780ac","tid":483954,"uid":50565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯絡舊post圖中人<br />\n不停兜圈 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n好明顯人地都唔知發生咩事，都要時間問清楚其他人<br />\n仲要係新人同個女仔都係去咗旅行<br />\n明明錢就比咗，冇啦啦話你比未錢，都要傾返同搵返到底咩事<br />\n睇多次wtsapp對話圖就知道唔係同一個人同阿伯傾啦<br />\n人地block你又話人地有問題，有個痴線佬係咁要求比錢交代本來比咗錢嘅事<br />\n唔block柒你就奇啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以其人之道 還治其人之身，咁鍾意公審，就係到同你玩，等個位呀Sam哥現身道歉！"},{"pid":"e1a6be4aedd84ac9bf5aac252fc815139d306c03","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/164435_1a06649437b1313cb99dc88f17064763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F164435_1a06649437b1313cb99dc88f17064763.jpg&h=bffeccdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我搞清楚喇<br />\n人地一早同你講話唔係香港，你就話人地block咗你電話<br />\n你地望多次張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/183755_4b7245aa70feeb43177fae4c07ce3de2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F183755_4b7245aa70feeb43177fae4c07ce3de2.jpg&h=b53fb627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左上角有飛航模式呀，點撚樣聽你電話呀阿sam哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己柒就柒啦，人地話係外地你唔撚信<br />\n一口咬地話人地block撚咗你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/003535_7e690afb2d20876d39b8cf4e28444396.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F003535_7e690afb2d20876d39b8cf4e28444396.png&h=2ad86c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地根本比人耍咗啦，阿sam哥仔自己柒咗就話係溝通有問題<br />\n你又比幾多時間人地去了解先？<br />\n係個group到講得唔清唔楚，而家係個group又唔見阿sam哥post呢兩張wtsapp上去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad30302f7fc3a35ac9ca87dac04a42ac90faaae","tid":483954,"uid":14021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一對新人同鍾小姐記得去完旅行要報警呀<br />\n被人爆私隱同誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"a3b13dbbb1d22ee76464a44e26d94f40322c2ed9","tid":483954,"uid":158975,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/164435_1a06649437b1313cb99dc88f17064763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F164435_1a06649437b1313cb99dc88f17064763.jpg&h=bffeccdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我搞清楚喇<br />\n人地一早同你講話唔係香港，你就話人地block咗你電話<br />\n你地望多次張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/183755_4b7245aa70feeb43177fae4c07ce3de2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F183755_4b7245aa70feeb43177fae4c07ce3de2.jpg&h=b53fb627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左上角有飛航模式呀，點撚樣聽你電話呀阿sam哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己柒就柒啦，人地話係外地你唔撚信<br />\n一口咬地話人地block撚咗你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/003535_7e690afb2d20876d39b8cf4e28444396.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F003535_7e690afb2d20876d39b8cf4e28444396.png&h=2ad86c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地根本比人耍咗啦，阿sam哥仔自己柒咗就話係溝通有問題<br />\n你又比幾多時間人地去了解先？<br />\n係個group到講得唔清唔楚，而家係個group又唔見阿sam哥post呢兩張wtsapp上去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛行模式個個唔係sam電話嚟<br />\n佢公司個高層"},{"pid":"1013bd3652a54f8e18e4612e9c1dc8deb9136fab","tid":483954,"uid":158975,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https: