錢<br />\n轉個頭就話係同個客溝通不良，佢地講完唔笑都幾好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"367fc36b56261471995ae070fc52ee9436ab89a7","tid":483954,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:48:49.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦 道歉都咁撚冇誠意仲講到自己冇錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e0fc94f110afb562e8242005d22ad9f66c0fda","tid":483954,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:02:18.000Z","msg":"交個老闆同上頭出黎"},{"pid":"b024e1633e56e4d64ac49e7efd946e070a8a907f","tid":483954,"uid":2567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:02:31.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦屌你老母，同你隻sam狗死返去facebook互含啦屌"},{"pid":"f1b715846f1e726316ede5913cbceca3b8492377","tid":483954,"uid":155080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"我年中book唔少旅遊巴，未聽過伍氏，以後都唔會用，亦會叫身邊D朋友唔好用，以免妨礙了伍氏咁精密嘅行政運作啦"}]}